### Day 5 – Assign Roles & Users to Certificate Group

#### 1. Accessing Groups
- Opened **ServiceNow**.  
- Clicked on **All → Search for Tables**.  
- Selected **Tables** under **System Definition**.  
- Selected the **Certificates Group**.  

#### 2. Assigning Users
- Under **Group Members**, clicked **Edit**.  
- Selected **Katherine Pierce**.  
- Clicked **Save**.  

#### 3. Assigning Roles
- Navigated to **Roles**.  
- Selected **Certification_role**.  
- Clicked **Save**.
